{"name":"Watch Company","size":"large","type":"Humanoid Group","tag":"","alignment":"neutral good","hitDice":"8","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"60 (8d10 + 16)","speedDesc":"80 ft. mounted, 30 ft standing.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"9","wisPoints":"13","chaPoints":"11","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"2","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The centaur can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The centaur regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the centaur can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the centaur can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The centaur can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the centaur's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the centaur's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the centaur dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Form Up!","desc":"Up to 10 allied watchpeople can move their speed towards [MON]. Each member of the formation gets a +5 to their AC."},{"name":"Surround Them!","desc":"The formation can move up to 30ft and surround up to 2 creatures."},{"name":"Nock... Loose!","desc":"[1d4]+1 watchpeople loose their arrows. Choose a point within 30ft, each creature within a 10ft sphere of the point must make a DC [DEX SAVE] dexterity save, or take [4d6+4] damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Baton","desc":"One watchperson in the formation, or [MON] makes a Baton attack"},{"name":"Crowd Control","desc":"[MON] can make a DC 12 Charisma check to calm or direct an unruly crowd."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Protect Civilans (2/round)","desc":"If a civilian is targeted by an attack, a watchperson may move their speed to leave the formation and interpose themselves to change the target of the attack to themselves."},{"name":"Scatter!","desc":"If a member of the formation takes damage, [MON] may issue a command and each member of the formation except [MON] can move up to their speed away from [MON]."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"The Captain","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}